Wine Mono is not vendored in this repository.

At `make image` build time, Dockerfile downloads the official MSI from:
  https://github.com/wine-mono/wine-mono/releases

Default version: 10.1.0 (build-arg WINE_MONO_VERSION in Dockerfile).
Override example:
  docker build --build-arg WINE_MONO_VERSION=11.0.0 -t wine-base .

License: COPYING in this directory (from upstream wine-mono/wine-mono).
Source tarballs: same GitHub releases page (wine-mono-*-src.tar.xz).
